{"tid":278444,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發！] 豬場新聞被Facebook Del咗","createTime":"2017-06-10T12:35:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-11T12:50:58.000Z","uid":92301,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"58d6988de45e4e7af4e3af74943823149a41ac32","tid":278444,"uid":92301,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T12:35:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/5h8u1927\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F5h8u1927&h=85ce8f6f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n日前收到 Facebook 通知，表示我地Page違反左 Facebook 社群規則，並將 Page 列為無法發佈狀態，豬場新聞除左即時提出申訴外，並即時電郵去信 Facebook香港及台灣公共政策總監表達申訴，希望解決問題。<br />\n<br />\n最近 Admin 出嘅 Post 都係正常批判香港社會各事嘅 post，並沒有刻意挑戰 Facebook 規則底線，對於今次 Facebook 行為豬場新聞Admin表示十分失望，過往選舉上我們均有積極地展開不同嘅討論，甚至社會運動前線作出圖文直播。豬場新聞運作三年當中曾經被檢舉過一次，失去數千過Like，如今達到2萬6個Like之時，疑似受到大量惡意檢舉，引致 Facebook 錯誤地引發機制。<br />\n<br />\n喺呢個言論自由受到各種挑戰嘅時代，豬場新聞不怕任何惡意打壓，望在 Facebook 呢個社交媒體戰場上為各位發聲。<br />\n<br />\n共勉之<br />\n------<br />\n現今我地選擇開啟後備Page，希望當日有Like過我地嘅人重新Like返，我地暫時可以做嘅就係咁多。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=862096997274310&amp;substory_index=0&amp;id=862088967275113\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D862096997274310%26substory_index%3D0%26id%3D862088967275113&d=P7KVl3aCdbmW02rc9LcTz57TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=6281e031\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=862096997274310&amp;substory_index=0&amp;id=862088967275113</a>"},{"pid":"a0e5f1e5fa087cc96a72fdb87dc49c98c3f833ce","tid":278444,"uid":92301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T12:57:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"faa9bccd69f373f67a94bf82aaa6f1750b803be3","tid":278444,"uid":12021,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T12:58:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bc3a91b00a40fadfedb2108cf7192064d254882e","tid":278444,"uid":22858,"like":0,